00:02:50.450 --> 00:02:54.299
You Only Live Twice

00:02:54.299 --> 00:02:58.519
The only thing as famous as this James Bond
movie's villain is his signature white cat.

00:02:58.519 --> 00:03:03.629
But even if Blofeld managed to keep his cool
while his base was overrun, the cat was a

00:03:03.629 --> 00:03:07.090
different story. Apparently nobody thought
about what would happen once an explosion

00:03:07.090 --> 00:03:11.720
was set off next to the animal, which means
audiences can watch as the cat loses its mind

00:03:11.720 --> 00:03:15.909
in real time, forcing actor Donald Pleasence
to keep it in a death grip just to get through

00:03:15.909 --> 00:03:19.879
